---
title: Cheese-Stuffed Tortellini Mac-n-Cheese with Crispy Shallot Topping
description: This rich, delicious mac-n-cheese uses cheese tortellini instead of elbow pasta, and we've topped this one with crispy shallots. Perfect for nights when you're craving comfort food.

